videos.description: Dwayne Haskins throws a perfect 38-yard bomb to Johnnie Dixon to open up Ohio State's scoring.
videos.headline: Haskins hits Dixon for 38-yard TD

videos.description: Dwayne Haskins hits Parris Campbell for the second Ohio State touchdown of the afternoon, putting the Buckeyes up 14-0.
videos.headline: Haskins connects with Campbell for 16-yard TD

videos.description: Dwayne Haskins finds Luke Farrell for a 9-yard touchdown. It's Haskins' third touchdown pass of the day.
videos.headline: Haskins throws 3rd TD of game for OSU

videos.description: Tate Martell finds Terry McLaurin with the perfect pass to put Ohio State up 28-0.
videos.headline: Martell's 51-yard dime gives OSU another TD

videos.description: J.K. Dobbins runs the ball into the end zone to extend Ohio State's lead to 35-0.
videos.headline: Dobbins runs 2 yards for another Buckeyes TD

videos.description: Dwayne Haskins throws another perfect pass to Johnnie Dixon for a 44-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Haskins' 4th TD of the day goes to Dixon
